                                            </li>
                                            <li><a href="https://medicalsaunas.com/" class="anchor-q"> <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0897/8953/0400/files/envelope.png?v=1737961714" class="call-width" alt=""> support@medicalsaunas.com</a></li>
